file: tmp_【＃癒月ちょこ生誕祭2023】ちょこ先生はてぇてぇに囲まれたい【ホロライブ⧸癒月ちょこ】 [r8DrUubFFCQ]_gemini-3-flash-preview/reencoded/part_000.mov

scenes.description: Opening splash screen for the Yuzuki Choco Birthday Live 2023.
Intro montage featuring various Hololive members in puzzle piece graphics.
Yuzuki Choco performs the song 'NoDistance' on a 3D stage.

subtitles.original: ちょこ先生はてぇてぇに囲まれたい ～癒月ちょこ生誕祭2023～
subtitles.english: Choco-sensei wants to be surrounded by 'Teetee' ~Yuzuki Choco Birthday Celebration 2023~

subtitles.original: Are you ready?
subtitles.english: Are you ready?

subtitles.original: NoDistance 作詞・作曲：涼木シンジ (KEYTONE)
subtitles.english: NoDistance / Lyrics & Composition: Shinji Suzuki (KEYTONE)

subtitles.original: 言葉を並べては　見なほら、ララヤ
subtitles.english: Words lined up, see? La la ya.

subtitles.original: 理屈だなんて　ゴミ箱へ
subtitles.english: Logics and such, into the trash.

subtitles.original: 身に覚えあるんでしょう　アンサー
subtitles.english: You have a vague idea, don't you? Answer.

subtitles.original: チク、チク、痛いのね
subtitles.english: Prick, prick, it hurts, doesn't it?

subtitles.original: エゴイズムに踊らされて
subtitles.english: Dancing to the tune of egoism.

subtitles.original: 蝕まれていく　アレ？アレ？
subtitles.english: Being eaten away. Oh? Oh?

subtitles.original: 地に焼き付けて　悪までも
subtitles.english: Sear it into the ground, even for evil.

subtitles.original: 癒してあげましょう　お目覚めですか？
subtitles.english: Let me heal you. Are you awake?

subtitles.original: Ding Dong Ding Dong　響かせ Ding Dong
subtitles.english: Ding Dong Ding Dong, let it echo, Ding Dong.

subtitles.original: 笑いな　ハッハッ　吐き捨てて
subtitles.english: Laugh, ha-ha, spit it out.

subtitles.original: Ding Dong Ding Dong　鳴らせよ Ding Dong
subtitles.english: Ding Dong Ding Dong, ring it, Ding Dong.

subtitles.original: 病むのが先か　止むのが先か
subtitles.english: Will you break first? Or will it stop first?

subtitles.original: 噛みつきゃしないわ
subtitles.english: I'm not going to bite you.

subtitles.original: 慰めもしないわ
subtitles.english: I'm not going to comfort you either.

subtitles.original: 私のものね
subtitles.english: You belong to me, don't you?

subtitles.original: 飽きたら　NoDistance
subtitles.english: When you're bored, NoDistance.

subtitles.original: 闇に紛れ甘いチョコレート捨てて
subtitles.english: Hiding in the dark, throw away the sweet chocolate.

subtitles.original: 古びた鎖繋いではくどいて
subtitles.english: Connecting old chains, courting.

subtitles.original: 仮の姿化けて瞳を貸して
subtitles.english: Disguising yourself, lend me your eyes.

subtitles.original: 傷が痛むのね
subtitles.english: The wound hurts, doesn't it?

subtitles.original: メカニズムに踊らされて
subtitles.english: Dancing to the tune of the mechanism.

subtitles.original: 失われていく　アレ？アレ？
subtitles.english: Fading away. Oh? Oh?

subtitles.original: 間違えても正しくても
subtitles.english: Whether you're wrong or right.

subtitles.original: 妖してあげましょう　あ、まだ
subtitles.english: Let me bewitch you. Oh, not yet...

subtitles.original: ダメですか？
subtitles.english: ...is it no good?

subtitles.original: Ding Dong Ding Dong　狂わせ Ding Dong
subtitles.english: Ding Dong Ding Dong, drive them crazy, Ding Dong.

subtitles.original: 最後に　ハッハッ　吐き捨てて
subtitles.english: In the end, ha-ha, spit it out.

subtitles.original: Ding Dong Ding Dong　鳴らせよ Ding Dong
subtitles.english: Ding Dong Ding Dong, ring it, Ding Dong.
